{"tid":1697223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日7/11 HDI 赤腳行大家點睇","createTime":"2019-11-06T16:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:43:18.000Z","uid":259116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"351beca8ba46260b0ff85c51035e5c931ce367b3","tid":1697223,"uid":259116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"想知大家有咩睇法 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好去<br />\n<br />\n原po:<br />\n同學對於呢個活動意見兩極化<br />\n<br />\n加上今日收到通知，嚟緊一個星期HKDI都係會停課嘅關係，宣傳非常困難，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHKDI 赤腳行 改為 7/11 星期四<br />\n<br />\n經前晚同 HKDI 同學討論 及 赤腳勘探 路線後,<br />\n1) 路徑大部份為單車徑和緩步跑徑, 少量石屎路<br />\n2) 海濱海岸絕大部份有工程進行, 海岸工程由大半年前開始至今未完工<br />\n3) 海岸工程附近道路有沙石<br />\n4) 小心留意路上沙石, 可減少受傷流血機會, 但不擔保可以完全不受傷流血<br />\n5) 路程約30-40分鐘<br />\n6) 赤腳步行的痛楚因人而異, 如中途不能承受可清潔後著鞋<br />\n*****有舉足輕重嘅疑點 同 線索, 不會在此說明, 請您除鞋行入去尋找*****<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uayyS6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuayyS6k.jpg&h=561285c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUiSpdm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUiSpdm.jpg&h=139017b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7672b479a33fbaeb84c1f443de3fabf534ff143e","tid":1697223,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:52:47.000Z","msg":"[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7746e475171af7277e6a94ddee5d22dd09bad616","tid":1697223,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ea1c990898e73143b023acd20c544b219efe944","tid":1697223,"uid":11277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"宣傳不足"},{"pid":"339e2d5a876f0d83869c141c2bd394bca796be34","tid":1697223,"uid":11277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"6715ff22971f35fd6360e1f200368478ef930aa6","tid":1697223,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:43:18.000Z","msg":"個活動好似冇曬消息咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陳彥霖</span><br />\n一個想自己第時小朋友有未來的小女孩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CKja0oT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCKja0oT.jpg&h=5b58b41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span></div><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ch.yinlam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fch.yinlam&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=ccaa09d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ch.yinlam</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n唔可以俾陳彥霖事件不了了之<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[重要發現] 陳彥霖事件討論分析(多圖)<br />\n</span><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg